=== 銷售 ===

在日本，《皮克敏3》是發售該週當中最暢銷的遊戲，上市兩天內即售出約9萬3千套的遊戲，並帶動售出約2.2萬台的Wii U主機。<ref>{{Cite web|title=This Week In Sales: Pikmin 3 And Luigi Lift Wii U Sales|url=https://www.siliconera.com/this-week-in-sales-pikmin-3-and-luigi-lift-wii-u-sales/|accessdate=2020-08-05|date=2013-07-17|work=Siliconera|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200825074728/https://www.siliconera.com/this-week-in-sales-pikmin-3-and-luigi-lift-wii-u-sales/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在英國，該遊戲首發週位居第二位，僅次於[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]版《[[我的世界|我的世界]]》零售版之後。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Pikmin 3 Makes UK Chart Debut in Second Place|url=https://www.nintendolife.com/news/2013/07/pikmin_3_makes_uk_chart_debut_in_second_place|accessdate=2020-08-05|date=2013-07-29|last=Life|first=Nintendo|work=Nintendo Life|language=en-GB|archive-date=2018-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180904080353/http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2013/07/pikmin_3_makes_uk_chart_debut_in_second_place|dead-url=no}}</ref>在美國，本作為首周銷量最高的遊戲，根據[[NPD集团|NPD Group]]的數據統計，該遊戲在上市的第一個月就售出了約11萬5千套。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Madden, Saints Row Top August 2013 NPD Charts, 3DS Sales Strong|url=https://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2013/09/12/madden-saints-row-top-npd-charts-3ds-sales-strong.aspx|accessdate=2020-08-05|last=Helgeson|first=Matt|work=Game Informer|language=en|archive-date=2019-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190828064528/https://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2013/09/12/madden-saints-row-top-npd-charts-3ds-sales-strong.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>截至2017年7月，本作在全球已售出117萬5458套。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Pikmin 3 for Wii U - Sales, Wiki, Release Dates, Review, Cheats, Walkthrough|url=https://www.vgchartz.com/|accessdate=2020-08-05|work=VGChartz|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804230456/https://www.vgchartz.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

